    public class BaseDStabBusImpl<TGen extends DStabGen,TLoad extends DStabLoad>
extends BaseAcscBusImpl<TGen,TLoad>
implements BaseDStabBus<TGen,TLoad>
    An implementation of the model object 'DStab Bus'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Init Load
    • Init Volt Mag
    • Load Model Switched
    • Freq
    • Bus Freq Measure Block
    • Dynamic Event
    • Info Only Dyn Model
    • Dynamic Bus Device List
